(1646, 29, '_o-nas-text-en_1_foto-o-nas-en', 'field_59268a71d8c9a'),
(1647, 29, 'o-nas-text-en_1_o-nas-title-en', 'WHAT ARE WE UNIQUE?'),
(1648, 29, '_o-nas-text-en_1_o-nas-title-en', 'field_59268c235eb82'),
(1649, 29, 'o-nas-text-en_1_text-o-nas-en', 'The cosmetic brand ELIER is based on Peloid Complex® - a balanced complex of active ingredients of high-organic mud Elier. In Peloid Complex® in high concentration contains active components: amino acids, vitamins, enzymes, phytohormones, minerals, micro- and macro elements, natural oxidants and antibiotics. Studies have shown that all elements present in the highly organic Peloid Complex® are present in skin cells. Skin cells are easily recognizable and fully accept a harmoniously balanced Peloid Complex®. This ensures structural compatibility with skin components and molecular level of exposure. As a result of exposure to Peloid Complex®, skin renewal occurs through self-healing.\r\n\r\nЭто единственный и неповторимый ресурс в мире!'),
(1650, 29, '_o-nas-text-en_1_text-o-nas-en', 'field_59268a71d8c9b'),
