(2260, 274, '_o-nas-text-en_0_foto-o-nas-en', 'field_59268a71d8c9a'),
(2261, 274, 'o-nas-text-en_0_o-nas-title-en', 'LUXURY DESIGN'),
(2262, 274, '_o-nas-text-en_0_o-nas-title-en', 'field_59268c235eb82'),
(2263, 274, 'o-nas-text-en_0_text-o-nas-en', 'The design was developed by one of the most remarkable designers of France - Jean-Michel Hostal, who created the design for Lancome and Clinique. The packaging was produced in France, in the same factories where the packaging for La Prairie and Helena Rubinstein is being created. The ELIER logo was a tree stylized as a woman''s profile. The sign is designed to symbolize the unity of nature and man.\r\n\r\nSCIENTIFICALLY BASIC TECHNOLOGIES\r\n\r\nFormulas of ELIER products were developed in cooperation with scientific laboratories. In Switzerland, ELIER Laboratory developed a unique ELIER Peloid Complex®. For more than 10 years, ELIER Laboratory has explored the unique properties of ELIER at the Samara State Medical University at the Department of Basic Biochemistry so that the whole world could use ELIER.'),
(2264, 274, '_o-nas-text-en_0_text-o-nas-en', 'field_59268a71d8c9b'),
(2265, 274, 'o-nas-text-en_1_foto-o-nas-en', '255'),
(2266, 274, '_o-nas-text-en_1_foto-o-nas-en', 'field_59268a71d8c9a'),
(2267, 274, 'o-nas-text-en_1_o-nas-title-en', 'WHAT ARE WE UNIQUE?'),
(2268, 274, '_o-nas-text-en_1_o-nas-title-en', 'field_59268c235eb82'),
(2269, 274, 'o-nas-text-en_1_text-o-nas-en', 'The cosmetic brand ELIER is based on Peloid Complex® - a balanced complex of active ingredients of high-organic mud Elier. In Peloid Complex® in high concentration contains active components: amino acids, vitamins, enzymes, phytohormones, minerals, micro- and macro elements, natural oxidants and antibiotics. Studies have shown that all elements present in the highly organic Peloid Complex® are present in skin cells. Skin cells are easily recognizable and fully accept a harmoniously balanced Peloid Complex®. This ensures structural compatibility with skin components and molecular level of exposure. As a result of exposure to Peloid Complex®, skin renewal occurs through self-healing.\r\n\r\nЭто единственный и неповторимый ресурс в мире!'),
(2270, 274, '_o-nas-text-en_1_text-o-nas-en', 'field_59268a71d8c9b'),
