(2274, 274, '_o-nas-text-en_2_o-nas-title-en', 'field_59268c235eb82'),
(2275, 274, 'o-nas-text-en_2_text-o-nas-en', 'ELIER is a group of companies with a wide vision and vision. Since 1996, ELIER has been producing products for beauty and rehabilitation with a solid goal in a harmonious way with nature to make the world more beautiful. The second most important line of business is business on recommendation, as we firmly believe that this is the most correct way to tell about our product. Working in these areas, ELIER allows people to highlight their personal characteristics, to open and develop unlimited potential, to gain self-confidence to open up to the world and emphasize their beauty and youth.\r\n\r\nELIER is committed to providing all women and men in the world with high-quality, high-organic cosmetics that conforms to the world standards of cosmetic production, provides unequivocal results and pleasure from use. In addition, everyone can share their impressions and develop their business by purchasing an ELIER franchise or using other forms of cooperation.'),
