(4294, 310, 'bdk-main-text-en', '[:ru]<h2>What is BDK Laboratory?</h2>\r\nBDK Laboratory™ is one of the oldest Latvian brands of organic cosmetics, which offers the necessary therapeutic and preventive products programs that will help you look beautiful and also feel good!\r\n<h2>What is unique cosmetics BDK Laboratory?</h2>\r\nAt the heart of cosmetics BDK Laboratory™ uses a unique vysokogoskii Elier mud, which was formed over 10 million years in the process of decomposition of elements of flora and fauna. In their structure contains all the nutrients needed by the body, including selenium, water of life, as well as biologically active organic matter, which makes the mud unique and unique natural health-improving complex. BDK Laboratory™, based on over 200 years of experience in the use of organic muds, developed Peloid Complex® in which the balance of essential amino acids, vitamins, enzymes, micro and macro elements, natural antibiotics and antioxidants found in organic muds and essential to the human body. Thanks to Peloid Complex®, the BDK Laboratory™ makes the challenge of science and contemporary cosmetic products for skin care.\r\n<h2>Peloid Complex®</h2>\r\nPeloid Complex® – the balance of active ingredients vysokoergonomichnoy dirt. Peloid Complex® contains amino acids, vitamins, enzymes, microelements, natural antibiotics and antioxidants. Studies have proven that all the elements present in vysokoergonomichnoy dirt is in the skin cells. Skin cells easily recognize and fully trust the harmonically balanced Peloid Complex®.\r\n\r\nthe 5-stage technology of extraction of Peloid Complex® is extracted vysokogoskii substances of high concentration – enzymes, enzymes, amino acids, vitamins, trace elements, which affect deeper layers of tissues, strengthen the immune system of the body, promote the natural process of the correct functioning of the organism, remove toxins and act as a powerful antioxidant.[:]'),
