(4351, 324, 'bdk-main-text-en', '[:ru]<h2>What is BDK Laboratory?</h2>\r\nBDK Laboratory™ is one of the oldest Latvian brands of organic cosmetics, which offers the necessary therapeutic and preventive products programs that will help you look beautiful and also feel good!\r\n<h2>What is unique cosmetics BDK Laboratory?</h2>\r\nAt the heart of cosmetics BDK Laboratory™ uses a unique vysokogoskii Elier mud, which was formed over 10 million years in the process of decomposition of elements of flora and fauna. In their structure contains all the nutrients needed by the body, including selenium, water of life, as well as biologically active organic matter, which makes the mud unique and unique natural health-improving complex. BDK Laboratory™, based on over 200 years of experience in the use of organic muds, developed Peloid Complex® in which the balance of essential amino acids, vitamins, enzymes, micro and macro elements, natural antibiotics and antioxidants found in organic muds and essential to the human body. Thanks to Peloid Complex®, the BDK Laboratory™ makes the challenge of science and contemporary cosmetic products for skin care.\r\n<h2>Peloid Complex®</h2>\r\nPeloid Complex® – the balance of active ingredients vysokoergonomichnoy dirt. Peloid Complex® contains amino acids, vitamins, enzymes, microelements, natural antibiotics and antioxidants. Studies have proven that all the elements present in vysokoergonomichnoy dirt is in the skin cells. Skin cells easily recognize and fully trust the harmonically balanced Peloid Complex®.\r\n\r\nthe 5-stage technology of extraction of Peloid Complex® is extracted vysokogoskii substances of high concentration – enzymes, enzymes, amino acids, vitamins, trace elements, which affect deeper layers of tissues, strengthen the immune system of the body, promote the natural process of the correct functioning of the organism, remove toxins and act as a powerful antioxidant.[:en]WHAT IS BDK LABORATORY?\r\n\r\nBDK Laboratory ™ is one of the oldest brands of Latvian organic cosmetics that offers the necessary therapeutic products and preventative programs that will help you look beautiful and feel good too!\r\n\r\nWHAT IS THE UNIQUE BDK LABORATORY COSMETICS?\r\n\r\nAt the heart of BDK Laboratory ™ cosmetics is the unique high-organic Elier mud, which has been formed for 10 million years in the process of decomposition of elements of flora and fauna. Their structure contains all the micronutrients necessary for the body, including selenium, living water, as well as biologically active organic substances, which makes the mud a unique and unique natural health complex. BDK Laboratory ™, based on more than 200 years of experience in the use of organic mud, has developed Peloid Complex®, which balances essential amino acids, vitamins, enzymes, micro and macro elements, natural antibiotics and antioxidants that are part of organic mud and are essential for the human body. Thanks to Peloid Complex®, BDK Laboratory ™ makes a challenge to science and modern cosmetics for skin care.\r\n\r\nPELOID COMPLEX®\r\n\r\nPeloid Complex® is a balance of active ingredients of highly organic mud. Peloid Complex® contains amino acids, vitamins, enzymes, microelements, natural antibiotics and antioxidants. Studies have shown that all elements present in highly organic mud are present in skin cells. Skin cells are easily recognized and fully trusted in the harmoniously balanced Peloid Complex®.\r\n\r\nThanks to 5-step extraction technologies, highly concentrated substances - enzymes, enzymes, amino acids, vitamins, microelements, are extracted from Peloid Complex®, which act on the deep layers of tissues, strengthen the body''s immune system, promote the natural process of proper functioning of the body, remove toxins and act as A powerful antioxidant.[:]'),
