was very interesting, and the second part of the Seminar gave me a lot that I could apply the knowledge of psychology in their business practices.\r\n\r\nEach workshop introduces the news, allows you to open a new vision. The knowledge we receive on any seminar, any training and activities are endless. Always after the Seminar I read his notes and try to think, to digest what I heard. A very important conclusion for me was the idea that a leader should be intelligent, decent, tactful and have self-respect.\r\n\r\nCome to seminars, congresses and training ELIER![:]', '[:ru]АКЦИЯ! ПОКУПАЯ ЛЮБОЙ ПРОДУКТ PROFЛИНИИ — ВТОРОЙ В ПОДАРОК!![:en]STOCK! BUYING ANY PROFILE PRODUCT - SECOND AS A GIFT !![:]', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nazvanie-stati-1', '', '', '2017-05-29 13:15:08', '2017-05-29 10:15:08', '', 0, 'http://mywebsite.mcdir.ru/eliergizer/?p=83', 0, 'post', '', 0),
