e in this process, we need to be at the Workshop, it''s important and it''s interesting. Very interesting was the Academy of Leaders is what can and need to learn.\r\n\r\nIrena.\r\n\r\nThe September Seminar for me was very instructive. Today is Monday, but I think all the time about what was seen and heard at the Seminar. Received a great deal of material for thought about how to work out how to develop. The very strong impressions I got from the speech. Canals on Academy Leaders, from his mental approach to business and business management. I concluded that for the successful development of your business, you need to work hard to get rid of previously acquired psychological problems. Well, next to me there are people with whom I can discuss, to speak, all I heard at the Seminar, my Business Partners.\r\n\r\nNeed to go to every Seminar because the information is always new, never sounds the same. If you want to be in business take part each time, and each time you get something new and important for your business and for your income.\r\n\r\nElena Skutelsky\r\n\r\nThe workshop was very warm and very homey. A very interesting speech. Canals – very bright and concentrated. She will definitely need it look at the types of leaders as each came to the Seminar draws from heard something important, necessary, new.\r\n\r\nKristina Niedrite\r\n\r\nThis time the Seminar is much deeper I realized that teaching another person can only be his example — such a conclusion, I once again made a speech Valentine''s day. I also realized how important a person''s attitude to business. I really liked the first part of the seminar because it was easy, relaxed, to allow people to think seriously, what the business is and what the ELIER business is business, and network marketing.\r\n\r\nAn important conclusion for me personally was the assertion that there is no need to lose time waiting for Business Partner will fill a list of contacts, you need to act immediately. Not only the first part